<sheets>
<sheet>
<plain>
<text x="203.2" y="58.42" size="1.778" layer="94">Note:  RX to CTS and TX to RTS 
doesn't make sense, but wired 
to allow breakout of ESP-01 RX 
and TX to a header if desired.
This board assumes a programmed
ESP-01 and can't be used with
the FTDI for in-circuit programming.</text>
<text x="264.16" y="7.62" size="1.778" layer="94">5</text>
<text x="182.88" y="25.4" size="1.778" layer="91">Note for rev 4:  Fix Top SS WP2, SDA, SCL placement.  
Fix Open Source HW logo placement
Added Board notch and Upper Left rounding
Added small top side pin labels</text>
</plain>
